User json
    ident            Text
    password         Text Maybe
    name             Text
    email            Email

    UniqueUser ident

    deriving Typeable Show

Building json
    name             Text
    description      Text
    created          UTCTime default=CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
    updated          UTCTime default=CURRENT_TIMESTAMP

    UniqueBuildingName name

    deriving Show

Room json
    building         BuildingId
    name             Text
    description      Text

    UniqueNameInBuilding name building

    deriving Show

ItemType json
    name             Text

    UniqueItemTypeName name

    deriving Show

Item json
    name             Text
    serialNumber     Text
    fundingSource    Text
    itemType         ItemTypeId
    currentCheckIn   CheckIn Maybe 

    deriving Show

ItemTypeProperty json
    name             Text
    itemType         ItemTypeId

    deriving Show

ItemProperty json
    value            Text
    itemTypeProperty ItemTypePropertyId
    item             ItemId

    deriving Show

CheckIn json
    item             ItemId
    room             RoomId
    date             UTCTime
    user             UserId

    deriving Show
